        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DetailedOutput\">A cone of icy shards bursts from your spread hands and coats the target in a layer of frost. You deal 2d4 cold damage to creatures in the area; they must each attempt a Reflex save.<br><br><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature takes no damage.<br><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage.<br><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage and takes a –5-foot status penalty to its Speeds for 2 rounds.<br><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage and takes a –10-foot status penalty to its Speeds for 2 rounds.</span></p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage increases by 2d4.&nbsp;</p>"
